text: I visit this clinic for my annual health checkup. They offer very comprehensive packages and deliver results in a timely and secure manner. The doctor takes the time to review the report in detail with you. The staff is also tremendously friendly and helpful!

This is my repeat visit here to do the AHT. Called the clinic to confirm the opening hours before coming. Came at 2.20pm on a Thursday so there was no queue at all. Dr Mark Chin was polite and objective. Test results came out in 10 minutes. Swift and no frills. Honestly don't quite understand the low ratings here haha.
Dr Kwek is very nice and understanding. It was new year eve and the clinic is suppose to close early. Though busy, i only waited for a few minutes.
Opening at 8am30 with a doctor arriving at 9am. I guess I should feel glad that the clerk said it upfront

Convenient clinic thatâ€™s located in Tanjong Pagar plaza. Contrary to the other negative reviews, my experience there was pleasant.

Receptionists were polite and prompt. Dr Kwek conducted the consultation in a non hurried manner and was patient and detailed in explaining.
